U.K. Stocks Erase Losses as Mining Shares Rally in London; BP Retreats

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-03-29T14:15:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/u-k-stocks-erase-losses-as-mining-shares-rally-in-london-bp-retreats.html
U.K. stocks erased losses, as a
rally in mining companies offset losses at BP Plc.  The FTSE 100 Index was little changed at 5,903.67 at 3:12
p.m. in  London  after earlier falling as much as 0.4 percent.  BHP Billiton Ltd., Lonmin Plc and Vedanta Resources Plc all
gained at least 1.7 percent. BP limited gains on the FTSE 100,
falling 2.2 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sarah Jones at 
 sjones35@bloomberg.net  